long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily send links from your browser to a Discord channel using this plugin! With just a right-click on any link, you can send it directly to your Discord channel via a webhook. No more copy-pasting or switching between windows, just seamless sharing.

To use this plugin, simply set up a webhook for your Discord channel and add it to the plugin's settings. From there, you can right-click on any link and select "Post to Discord" to share it with your channel.

Features:

Simple and easy to use
Saves time by eliminating the need to switch between windows
Compatible with any Discord channel that has a webhook set up
We hope you enjoy using Discord Webhook Link Sender!
